explain: One of the factors your CIBIL Score depends on is your credit activity. Every time you apply for a credit card/loan, the lender/credit institution makes an enquiry, which is captured in your CIBIL Report. A high number of such enquiries in the last 36 months will impact your CIBIL Score. Ensure your CIBIL Score is not impacted negatively by your credit activity.
